                    <cell cols="2">
                        <hi rendition="#aq">b.</hi> Alt-Engli&#x017F;ch-Canada, Neu-Schottland,<lb/>Labrador ......... </cell>
                    <cell>260,000.</cell>
                </row>
                <lb/>
